data.description: Beautiful landscaped 2-story 4 bedroom home built in 2022.  Includes a porch and patio covered area. Home has a Large open concept, ceramic tile, granite counter tops, a beautiful modern style kitchen with an island, recessed lighting throughout. Every room has their own walk in closet, plus a Loft area which is located upstairs. Pictures include floor plan. Home has above ground pool, Security cameras are paid off and will convey with the sale of the home. Has turf in the front and back of the home. Storage shed and Grill will also convey. Garage has a split unit with AC & heating. Extended rock wall to 6ft for more privacy.
